19:34.660 --> 19:36.100
Not him,Devalos.

19:36.110 --> 19:39.100
Something bad was going
to happen to Devalos.

19:39.110 --> 19:40.910
What do you mean "bad"?

19:40.920 --> 19:42.470
I don't know.

19:42.480 --> 19:44.430
His friend was in cahoots with Van Dyke.

19:44.440 --> 19:47.560
They were plotting against Devalos.

19:47.570 --> 19:49.900
What do you mean?
Plotting against him how?

19:49.910 --> 19:52.060
I don't know.

19:53.480 --> 19:56.690
So you met this guy, and you
got a bad feeling about him.

19:56.700 --> 19:58.190
Then what happened?

19:58.200 --> 20:01.980
Well,then he wrote Devalos a big check.

20:01.990 --> 20:07.860
Well,I'm no politico, but there must be a better
way to crush a campaign than by funding it.

20:11.660 --> 20:13.250
So did you say something to him?

20:13.260 --> 20:14.690
Well,say wh||?

20:16.400 --> 20:19.570
The night seemed to be
going so well for him.

20:19.580 --> 20:22.170
I didn't want to be the one to ruin it.

20:24.240 --> 20:27.650
Especially since I don't know
what, if anything,is going on.

20:29.150 --> 20:33.760
All right,we have 45 minutes
before the girls get up.

20:33.770 --> 20:37.570
Oh,did you happen to see the note that
I left for you in the kitchen last night?

20:37.580 --> 20:40.460
The message from Scanlon?

20:41.730 --> 20:45.300
You know,I don't get it. I'm usually
persona non grata around here.

20:46.470 --> 20:49.150
You know,you're sneaking
around to meet me, but today,

20:49.160 --> 20:52.180
you're waiting for me by the front
door, escorting me up the elevator.

20:52.190 --> 20:52.820
What can I tell you?

20:52.830 --> 20:56.620
If I had my way,we'd pick you up in a limo,
offer you champagne and caviar for lunch.

20:56.630 --> 20:59.440
You know,don't you worry if you lie
like that, your nose is going to grow?

20:59.450 --> 21:01.320
Or God's going to
smite you or something?

21:01.330 --> 21:02.660
Look,the honest to God truth is,

21:02.670 --> 21:06.140
I got two dead 20-something guys who were
found exactly where you said they'd be,

21:06.150 --> 21:08.650
murdered exactly the
way you said they'd be.

21:08.660 --> 21:10.530
I need to get you with a sketch artist.

21:10.540 --> 21:12.070
I know it sounds like a lot of nothing.

21:12.080 --> 21:15.350
I just kind of felt funny
keeping it to myself.

21:15.360 --> 21:19.460
Well,I don't know what
to tell you,Allison.

21:19.470 --> 21:20.830
The man's check cleared.

21:20.840 --> 21:25.060
Well,at the end of the day, I guess
that's all that really matters.

21:29.750 --> 21:31.280
I'm being summoned.

21:31.290 --> 21:33.590
Oh,well,then don't let me keep you.

21:33.600 --> 21:35.930
You know,it meant a lot to me
that you were there last night,

21:35.940 --> 21:39.920
and for what it's worth, your name
was mentioned in this morning's paper.

21:39.930 --> 21:42.960
Well,then I guess it's
mission accomplished.

21:42.970 --> 21:44.070
Mission accomplished.

21:44.080 --> 21:45.910
I'll talk to you soon.

21:48.080 --> 21:52.780
You know,it just doesn't make much
sense what she's saying, Mr. Devalos.

21:52.790 --> 21:54.850
It just... doesn't.

21:54.860 --> 21:57.530
Well,I grant you,it doesn't
make much sense to us.

21:57.540 --> 22:00.730
No,it doesn't make much sense,period.

22:00.740 --> 22:04.580
Why would Richard Madsen be having secret
meetings with District Attorney Van Dyke?

22:04.590 --> 22:06.950
The man just donated a
truckload of money to you.

22:06.960 --> 22:07.970
Well,then, you tell me.

22:07.980 --> 22:09.870
What kind of deal could
they have been making?

22:09.880 --> 22:10.880
Manny,listen to yourself.

22:10.890 --> 22:13.860
You're becoming completely preoccupied
because some woman told you ...

22:13.870 --> 22:15.440
Not some woman.

22:15.450 --> 22:18.370
Allison Dubois. Do me a favor.

22:18.380 --> 22:22.300
Just... keep your ear to the ground.

22:22.690 --> 22:24.390
Okay.

22:42.960 --> 22:43.740
Got your message.

22:43.750 --> 22:46.170
Dispatch said you think you
may have spotted my suspect.

22:46.180 --> 22:49.310
My partner and I got a call to
break up a fight in the parking lot.

22:49.320 --> 22:53.460
We were finishing up in here with the owner,
and I saw someone that looked like your sketch.

22:53.470 --> 22:55.930
She even has the coat.

23:04.940 --> 23:06.750
Hello.

23:07.760 --> 23:09.460
Sorry.

23:10.290 --> 23:12.740
- Hello?
- Am I waking you?

23:12.750 --> 23:14.200
No. It's okay.

23:14.210 --> 23:17.430
I think I may have spotted your exterminating
angel, that woman you keep dreaming about?

23:17.440 --> 23:20.190
She's here at a bar trolling
for guys half her age.

23:20.200 --> 23:21.350
You're kidding.

23:21.360 --> 23:23.410
No,Allison. It's 11:45.

23:23.420 --> 23:26.830
I never kid after 10:00 on a weeknight.

23:27.580 --> 23:29.960
So here's what I'm calling to find out.

23:29.970 --> 23:30.950
You had any more dreams?

23:30.960 --> 23:35.400
I mean,is this chick gonna pull a chainsaw out
of her purse or a jackhammer out of her underwear?

23:36.840 --> 23:39.410
Is there anything I should
be on the lookout for?

23:39.420 --> 23:40.340
I'm sorry. I don't know.

23:40.350 --> 23:42.770
I haven't had a dreamt about
her in the last couple days.

23:42.780 --> 23:46.180
Okay,well,I'm gonna take that as a good sign,
maybe introduce myself to this little lady,

23:46.190 --> 23:48.250
see if I can get to the
bottom of this thing.

23:48.260 --> 23:49.470
Okay.

23:49.480 --> 23:51.400
- All right.
- Bye.

23:56.550 --> 24:01.440
I no,uh, speaka da English
so... so good,yeah,no.

24:01.450 --> 24:04.200
You speaka da English just fine.

24:04.210 --> 24:07.180
Oh,pretty. Oh,yeah.Yeah.

24:07.190 --> 24:12.580
Maybe,um, I-I teach
you Italiano later,huh?

24:16.220 --> 24:18.170
Excuse me? Excuse me!Phoenix PD.

24:18.180 --> 24:20.390
Ma'am,if I could ask you to please
step away from the gentleman.

24:20.400 --> 24:21.690
Keep your hands where I can see them.

24:21.710 --> 24:23.180
What's this all abou|| What's going on?

24:23.190 --> 24:24.600
It's about her,sir. It's not about you.

24:24.610 --> 24:26.290
If you could stand still and stay calm.

24:26.300 --> 24:30.310
I am not from here. Are you policia?

24:30.320 --> 24:31.370
Yeah. That's me.Policia.

24:31.380 --> 24:33.250
Tell you what. Why don't
you hand me the purse?

24:33.260 --> 24:34.610
Hand me the purse. Turn around.

24:34.620 --> 24:36.110
Put your hands on the car. Turn around.

24:36.120 --> 24:38.780
Put your hands on the car.

24:39.910 --> 24:41.810
Uh,scuzi? Scuzi?

24:43.610 --> 24:47.040
Says here,you're
Michelle Todd of Tucson.

24:47.310 --> 24:48.300
Okay.

24:48.310 --> 24:52.470
So,uh,is trying to impress a guy
in a bar against the law,Officer?

24:52.480 --> 24:54.170
Maybe.

24:54.180 --> 24:56.400
I think you're going to have
to come with me,Ms. Todd.

24:56.410 --> 24:58.250
What? I'm just a girl
looking to have some fun.

24:58.260 --> 25:00.790
- What's the crime?
- Murder.

25:01.090 --> 25:02.130
Well,wait a second.

25:02.140 --> 25:06.010
- What are you talking about?
- You ever had any contact with a Ryan Haas or Mr. Sean Covey?

25:06.020 --> 25:06.980
Who?

25:06.990 --> 25:08.260
Maybe you never asked them their names.

25:08.270 --> 25:10.240
A support group widower in
need of a little comfort?

25:10.250 --> 25:12.380
A bartender I suspect
you may have nailed?

25:12.390 --> 25:13.660
- You have the right to remain silent...
- Wait.

25:13.670 --> 25:14.840
Wait,wait. Wait a second.Wait a second!

25:14.850 --> 25:17.180
A bartender? Support group widowers?

25:17.190 --> 25:19.100
It sounds like you're talking
about my book. I have a...

25:19.110 --> 25:20.810
Ma'am,let's not make
this difficult,okay?

25:20.820 --> 25:22.710
No,no,look,look! Open my trunk.

25:22.720 --> 25:23.760
It sounds like my book!

25:23.770 --> 25:24.910
Open my trunk, and I'll show you!

25:24.920 --> 25:27.460
All right,all right,all right.

25:29.910 --> 25:31.990
If you take her for a second?

25:37.640 --> 25:43.920
A Cougar's Guide to the Hunt: Bagging a
Man in the Urban Jungle by Charisma Kennedy.

25:43.930 --> 25:45.760
Be nice. That's my pen name.

25:45.770 --> 25:48.700
Look,flip it over.
Look,see?That's my picture.

25:48.710 --> 25:49.500
It's beautiful.

25:49.510 --> 25:51.050
Thank you.

25:51.060 --> 25:54.010
See,in there...in there... Under
the chapter headings-- look,see?

25:54.020 --> 25:55.930
It's all there.

25:56.510 --> 25:59.520
"Making the Connection
at a Support Group."

26:00.120 --> 26:03.150
"Leaving More than a
Tip for the Bartender."

26:03.160 --> 26:05.400
Nothing in here about cops,huh?

26:05.410 --> 26:06.900
No. Why?

26:06.910 --> 26:08.240
Tonight's your lucky night.

26:08.250 --> 26:11.940
I'm going to take you downtown.

26:17.300 --> 26:19.840
I hate you. It's barely
7:00 in the morning.

26:19.850 --> 26:22.730
Hey,early bird,I thought you
wanted to catch this worm.

26:22.740 --> 26:25.500
Well,where is she? I've
been here since 6:00.

26:25.510 --> 26:28.450
Hold your horses. The
show is about to begin.

26:28.460 --> 26:31.420
Here comes your dream girl now.

26:37.710 --> 26:39.200
What do you think?

26:39.210 --> 26:40.440
Well,that's her.

26:40.460 --> 26:42.730
At least it looks like her.

26:43.670 --> 26:45.370
What's the hesitation about?

26:45.400 --> 26:47.300
I don't know. She looks so frightened.

26:48.000 --> 26:50.410
Well,being charged with
murder will do that to you.

26:50.420 --> 26:53.990
Hey,when you get a chance, if you have some
time, this is actually a pretty good read.

26:54.000 --> 26:56.350
Every seduction you ever
dreamed of is in here.

26:56.360 --> 26:58.690
The support group, the bartender.

26:58.700 --> 26:59.680
It's quite uncanny.

26:59.690 --> 27:02.680
What is this, a how-to
book for killing men?

27:02.690 --> 27:05.350
Not killing them,
Allison. Seducing them.

27:05.730 --> 27:08.980
Oh,you mean, there's no chapter in here
about the best way to nail-gun your man

27:08.990 --> 27:11.210
after he's flambéed you in the kitchen?

27:11.220 --> 27:13.900
Maybe she's saving that for the sequel.

27:14.830 --> 27:17.540
Let's go have a little chat.

27:17.940 --> 27:21.180
You both understand how absurd this is.

27:23.900 --> 27:25.960
I... Look at me!I-I...

27:25.970 --> 27:29.250
I don't even know how to
use a knife or a nail gun.

27:29.260 --> 27:31.710
I like men. In fact,I love them.

27:31.720 --> 27:34.120
I've made a lot of money loving them.

27:34.130 --> 27:35.290
How do you mean?

27:35.300 --> 27:38.350
Well, as Charisma
Kennedy, I have the books.

27:38.360 --> 27:40.400
I've written 12.

27:40.410 --> 27:42.540
That one came out four months ago.

27:42.560 --> 27:45.380
In fact,I'm still
doing the book signings.

27:45.400 --> 27:48.570
Then there's Charisma
Kennedy, the column and blog.

27:48.580 --> 27:52.630
Then as Michelle,I have The Single
Girl's Guide to Financial Independence.

27:52.640 --> 27:57.860
And then as John Todd,I have The Single
Guy's Guide to Financial Independence.

27:57.870 --> 28:01.760
I'm a busy little girl,
but I am no murderer.

28:01.770 --> 28:05.710
Then why don't you just tell us where
you were on the nights in question?

28:07.650 --> 28:09.080
Look,I don't mind
waiting for a couple hours

28:09.090 --> 28:12.320
until your lawyer gets into his
office and we can get him down here.

28:12.330 --> 28:13.350
No,really.

28:13.360 --> 28:14.970
I don't have anything to hide. I...

28:14.980 --> 28:18.530
It's just you're not
going to believe my alibi.

28:18.540 --> 28:19.080
What do you mean?

28:19.090 --> 28:22.420
Do you not remember what you were
doing on the nights in question?

28:22.430 --> 28:25.050
I remember exactly what I was doing.

28:25.080 --> 28:27.050
I was at home...

28:27.060 --> 28:28.870
alone... reading.

28:28.880 --> 28:31.820
I don't know.Based on
what I saw last night,

28:31.830 --> 28:35.330
you don't strike me as the
"home alone reading" type.

28:35.340 --> 28:37.800
Well,I am.

28:38.410 --> 28:40.390
For the most part.

28:40.410 --> 28:44.300
Sure,yeah,sometimes I have to go
out and see what's really going on.

28:44.310 --> 28:45.610
Hear the latest lines.

28:45.620 --> 28:48.310
Try a new technique.

28:48.320 --> 28:51.830
Is there a law against a single
girl looking to have some fun?

28:51.840 --> 28:54.150
You say that,but the fact
remains two men are dead.

28:54.160 --> 28:57.150
Well,I had nothing to do with it!

28:57.160 --> 28:58.910
I'm no killer.

28:58.930 --> 29:00.950
Like I said,I love men!

29:00.960 --> 29:04.970
But the fact remains two men have been murdered
using techniques eerily similar to not one,

29:05.000 --> 29:08.450
but two chapters in your book.

29:08.460 --> 29:12.550
Yeah,well,then, maybe it means
that your killer can read.

29:14.380 --> 29:17.020
Look,I'm going to make this
simple for you,Ms. Todd.

29:17.050 --> 29:19.520
If you can't provide us with an
alibi for the nights in question,

29:19.530 --> 29:22.760
then I'm gonna have to exercise
my right to hold you for 24 hours

29:22.780 --> 29:25.170
while I obtain a warrant
to search your apartment.

29:25.200 --> 29:26.470
But that's not right!

29:26.490 --> 29:29.600
Yeah,well... that's the law.

29:29.880 --> 29:30.530
But don't worry.

29:30.540 --> 29:35.650
I'll be sending a hot,young thing in
here in a minute to,uh,show you to a cell.

29:39.990 --> 29:41.820
Come in.

29:43.030 --> 29:44.310
Richard.

29:44.320 --> 29:46.700
Come on in. Take a seat.

29:49.380 --> 29:52.550
I'll just leave and
let you two catch up.

29:57.300 --> 30:00.140
So,you want to tell me about it?

30:00.150 --> 30:03.180
What... What are you
talking about,Manny?

30:04.030 --> 30:08.210
I got a message to come
see you, and here I am.

30:08.700 --> 30:12.860
It's your meeting. You want
an answer?Ask a question.

30:12.870 --> 30:16.130
Okay,here's a question.

30:16.140 --> 30:17.990
Did you know when I
was District Attorney,

30:18.000 --> 30:22.720
that some concerns surfaced about
corruption in the construction sector?

30:22.730 --> 30:24.900
No. I...I didn't know that.

30:24.910 --> 30:29.750
Didn't get very far before I was
asked to take a permanent vacation.

30:30.260 --> 30:33.310
But as it turns out, I still have some
friends in the District Attorney's office,

30:33.320 --> 30:37.430
and recently, they've brought
some information to my attention.

30:39.540 --> 30:42.860
Paying off city inspectors?

30:42.870 --> 30:44.390
Bribing council members?

30:44.410 --> 30:47.310
Van Dyke must have really
put the screws to you.

30:47.330 --> 30:49.210
I don't know what you're talking about,

30:49.230 --> 30:54.530
but this is a strange way to thank
a major contributor to your campaign.

30:55.230 --> 30:58.080
Yeah. Right.

30:58.480 --> 31:01.430
Thanks. So,how is that supposed to work?

31:01.440 --> 31:05.770
I cash the check, and then Van Dyke
announces that he's indicting you?

31:05.780 --> 31:09.220
And,oh,yes, isn't it funny that former
DA Manuel Devalos is taking money

31:09.230 --> 31:14.200
from a city contractor under
investigation for corruption and fraud?

31:14.210 --> 31:15.670
What did he promise you?

31:15.680 --> 31:19.900
A suspended sentence, some kind of fine?

31:21.610 --> 31:24.280
You're my friend,Manny.

31:24.290 --> 31:28.160
Y-You've always been my friend. I...

31:29.470 --> 31:32.380
I had no choice. I,uh...

31:34.130 --> 31:37.380
I can't go to jail.

31:42.530 --> 31:44.150
It was very strange.

31:44.160 --> 31:48.580
On one hand I had these very vivid
dreams, in which she was always the one.

31:48.590 --> 31:53.980
And then sitting across from her
today, my instincts told me I was wrong.

31:53.990 --> 31:56.660
Well,for God's sake,
listen to your instincts.

31:56.670 --> 31:58.030
Don't listen to your instincts.

32:01.370 --> 32:03.190
Well,she's in jail tonight.

32:03.200 --> 32:06.490
So,I guess it's up to the police
and the justice system now.

32:07.530 --> 32:09.210
Why are you scratching your ear?

32:10.160 --> 32:12.050
I don't know.

32:12.390 --> 32:15.720
I'm hoping it's just a case
of the power of suggestion.

32:15.730 --> 32:18.650
Hanging out with Marie all this
time, watching her scratch her ear.

32:19.940 --> 32:21.650
Well,I hope you're right.

32:21.660 --> 32:26.860
I will be very upset if I have to wake up early
in the morning and rush you to the pediatrician.

32:27.690 --> 32:30.240
Right back at you.

32:40.240 --> 32:41.550
Where you going?

32:41.560 --> 32:45.920
I told you. I have a transport at 0800.

32:46.610 --> 32:51.450
I'm shipping out to Germany for
a satellite operations assignment.

32:51.460 --> 32:54.190
So... last night was it?

32:54.200 --> 32:56.640
You turn me out and then you just leave?

32:56.650 --> 32:58.330
Honey,we agreed.

32:58.340 --> 32:59.740
No strings attached.

32:59.750 --> 33:01.130
No seeing each other again.

33:01.150 --> 33:03.790
Yeah,but that was before.

33:03.800 --> 33:06.880
I mean,this is kind of new to me,but...

33:06.890 --> 33:08.620
I don't want you to go.

33:08.630 --> 33:10.170
I'll tell you what.

33:10.180 --> 33:13.140
I'll give you something
special before I leave.

33:13.150 --> 33:15.980
Something to remember me by.

33:18.300 --> 33:19.870
Come here.

33:20.020 --> 33:21.830
What are you doing?

33:23.550 --> 33:26.610
You'll see. Give me your hand.

33:33.900 --> 33:35.620
There you go.

33:35.950 --> 33:37.760
Now the other.

33:39.610 --> 33:41.800
There you go.

33:46.520 --> 33:49.270
Now close your eyes.

33:53.050 --> 33:55.440
Lift your head.

34:08.500 --> 34:10.520
They're bringing her up right now.

34:10.530 --> 34:12.060
How is she?

34:12.070 --> 34:13.409
Relieved. Upset.

34:13.420 --> 34:15.239
Thrilled that she's starting
to look like she's not guilty.

34:15.250 --> 34:17.719
Horrified that somebody's doing this.

34:17.730 --> 34:18.900
I don't know what to tell you,Lee.

34:18.909 --> 34:20.860
In my dreams,I saw her.

34:20.870 --> 34:22.239
I saw her kill that man last night.

34:22.250 --> 34:23.860
I saw her kill all those men.

34:23.870 --> 34:26.110
Well,she definitely didn't kill
the guy you called about last night.

34:26.120 --> 34:29.380
She's been under lock and
key for the past 24 hours.

34:29.389 --> 34:34.719
Ms. Todd, I want to tell you that the Phoenix
Police Department extends its sincerest apologies.

34:35.130 --> 34:36.659
So,that's it?

34:36.670 --> 34:37.639
************

34:37.650 --> 34:41.639
********

34:41.650 --> 34:45.000
*********you are free to go.

34:49.690 --> 34:54.090
You know, my book has sold
upwards of 60,000 copies.

34:54.100 --> 34:55.320
Okay.

34:55.330 --> 34:59.690
Well,it seems to me that means there are at
least 60,000 people who could be doing this.

34:59.920 --> 35:02.960
Who could be using my book, my...

35:02.970 --> 35:06.810
techniques, the scenarios I've
written to lure young men into bed.

35:06.820 --> 35:08.540
Yeah,actually,I thought
about that myself.

35:08.550 --> 35:12.270
Except I couldn't find the setup for
last night's killing anywhere in here.

35:12.280 --> 35:14.400
- Really?
- Really.Here.

35:14.410 --> 35:17.090
We know that the killer was
dressed up as a naval officer.

35:17.100 --> 35:20.230
And there isn't any, anything
like that in the book.

35:20.240 --> 35:22.920
A naval officer?

35:22.930 --> 35:26.420
Oh,they told me they hated that one.

35:26.440 --> 35:28.150
I'm sorry. Who told you they hated what?

35:28.160 --> 35:29.560
My publisher.

35:29.590 --> 35:32.140
It was one of the scenarios
that was cut from my book.

35:32.150 --> 35:34.200
Uh,"Patriot Games" I think I called it.

35:34.210 --> 35:36.770
Female naval officer.It's her
last night before shipping off

35:36.780 --> 35:42.070
and she is going to spend it
sharing her bedroom secrets *******

35:42.630 --> 35:45.010
Um,are there any others?

35:45.020 --> 35:45.840
Sure.

35:45.850 --> 35:48.980
I remember they couldn't wait to get
rid of "Naughty Nun with a Bad Habit."

35:48.990 --> 35:52.780
It was like,who has a
nun's habit hanging around?

35:52.790 --> 35:54.880
Oh,and then there's "The Extra Ticket."

