38:24.490 --> 38:25.950
Okay.

38:48.150 --> 38:49.740
You work here?

38:49.750 --> 38:51.230
No. Just visiting.

38:51.240 --> 38:53.720
Are you an author?

38:54.090 --> 38:57.080
