39:42.590 --> 39:47.430
Ah,you'd be amazed at the number of
people, who otherwise would never...

39:48.070 --> 39:49.850
yeah,they're at a vulnerable moment.

39:49.860 --> 39:52.040
They're lonely. They're bored.

39:52.050 --> 39:53.760
In a strange city.

39:56.910 --> 40:00.300
It's just a basketball game.

40:01.160 --> 40:04.860
I've been told I'm terrific company.

40:05.640 --> 40:08.440
I promise you, I'm discreet.

40:08.450 --> 40:14.880
In fact,I think I can safely say that no one who's
