41:00.660 --> 41:04.130
I mean,it's obviously
a very effective book...

41:04.150 --> 41:06.680
maybe too effective.

41:08.960 --> 41:10.390
And what's next for you?

41:10.400 --> 41:14.360
Well,ironically,this tragedy has brought
