41:14.370 --> 41:18.490
I've gotten a number of calls from cable
networks about a Cougar reality show,

41:18.500 --> 41:23.590
and maybe a Cougar Web site or a social
networking,uh,page like My Cougar.

41:23.600 --> 41:27.040
And you know... I'm open to anything.

